<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Weather Search</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="weather.css">
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Weather Search</h1>

  <p>
    Stay prepared for any weather condition with our Weather Search feature. Simply enter the location you want to know the weather for, and let us provide you with up-to-date forecast information.
  </p>

  <h2>How it works:</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Enter location:</strong>
      Input the city you want to check the weather for. Whether it's your current city or a place you plan to visit, our Weather Search has you covered.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Get weather forecast:</strong>
      Click on the "Search" button to retrieve the current weather conditions as well as the forecast for the upcoming days. You'll get information on temperature, humidity, wind speed, and more.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Stay informed:</strong>
      Stay prepared for your outdoor activities or plan your trips accordingly by staying informed about the weather forecast. Our Weather Search helps you make better decisions based on real-time weather data.
    </li>
  </ol>

  <p>Start exploring the weather today with our Weather Search!</p>

  <%= form_with(url: weather_show_path, method: 'get', id: 'weather-form') do |form| %>
    <div class="form-group">
      <%= form.label :city, 'City:' %>
      <%= form.text_field :city, class: 'form-control', required: true %>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <%= form.label :country, 'Country:' %>
      <%= form.text_field :country, class: 'form-control', required: true %>
    </div>

    <%= form.submit 'Check the Weather', class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
  <% end %>
</body>
</html>
